parameters.name: BuyResourceIds
parameters.description: The IDs of the purchased IP instances. Separate multiple IDs with commas (,). You can obtain the instance IDs from the response of the DedicatedIpNonePoolList operation.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: The name of the IP pool. The name must be 1 to 50 characters in length. It can contain letters, digits, underscores (\_), and hyphens (-). The name cannot be changed after the IP pool is created.
